==English==
===Noun===
# The quality or state of being [[simultaneous]]; [[simultaneousness]].
# In music a '''simultaneity''' is more than one complete musical texture occuring at the same time. This first appeared in the music of [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Ives Charles Ives], and is common in the music of [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conlon_Nancarrow Conlon Nancarrow], and others.

